{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "21.1",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8a33626f",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "はー……！　ヒマヒマ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.3",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "8a33626f",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "なんで大人しくしてなきゃいけないのよ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.1",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f911fc52",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "というか、お宝ザクザクの宇宙船の中で静かにしている通りはないわね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.3",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "f911fc52",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "海賊らしく色々物色してやろうかしら……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.1",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6db95d3",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "でも下僕のヤツ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.3",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "6db95d3",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "船に手を出したら許さないって言ってたし……ここは大人しく……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.1",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c47f8efb",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "って！　なんで海賊の船長のあたしが、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.3",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "c47f8efb",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "下僕なんかの言う事を聞く必要があるのよ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.1",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "85b64faa",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "そもそも許さないって何よ……！　下僕の分際でぇっ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.1",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3684ec5d",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "あの生意気な下僕には徹底的に分からせる必要があるわね……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.3",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "3684ec5d",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "どこにいるのよ、{G_PlayerName}のヤツ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.0",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e75f0a2a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……ぶわっくっしょん！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "61.0",
      "line_index": 61,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "88283ef8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……うう、いきなりすげーくしゃみ出てしまったな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "61.2",
      "line_index": 61,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "88283ef8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "部屋の温度の設定が低いのかな……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.1",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "85061aad",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "どこにいるのよ下僕！　ていうか宇宙船広すぎっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.3",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "85061aad",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "どれだけ歩かせる気なのよっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "68.0",
      "line_index": 68,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e5b98b42",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──げっ！？　この声アイディル？　まためんどくさそーなヤツが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.0",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b75103f9",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "なんか叫んでるし、見なかったことにしよう……うん、それがいい",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.1",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1003dbef",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "あーーーっ！　やっと見つけたっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.0",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ae122418",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うげっ！？　見つかった！？　逃げろっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "90.1",
      "line_index": 90,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "27c5f54",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "あっ！　こら！　どこに行くのよ！　待ちなさいっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.0",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fe99d602",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "なっ！　なんで追いかけてくんだよっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "112.1",
      "line_index": 112,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3a3f04c0",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "うっさい！　あんたが逃げるからでしょ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "115.1",
      "line_index": 115,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1cd25c87",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "このあたしから逃げられると思わないことね！　この下僕め！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "118.1",
      "line_index": 118,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "cf60d2b7",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "うりゃーーーーっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.1",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "85e1d9d9",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "──ごはぁっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.1",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2da6cf70",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "ふっふーん♪　どう？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.3",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "2da6cf70",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "悪のカリスマセクシー船長キックのお味は？　あははははっ♪",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.0",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1732242e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……うぐ、ぐぐぐぐ……お、お前、人の背中に思いっきり蹴りを……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.2",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1732242e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "な、なんてヤツ……い、いてぇ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.1",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "cc16d5d6",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "うっさい！　口答えすんな！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.3",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "cc16d5d6",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "下僕の分際で船長から逃げるからお仕置きしただけよっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.0",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bf914b32",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お仕置きって……俺が何したんだよ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.2",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "bf914b32",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "まったく……あー……これ絶対背中に足跡思いっきり付いてるぞ……くう、いてぇ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "144.1",
      "line_index": 144,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4c73a3a7",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "はぁっ！？　このあたしから逃げたでしょうが！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "144.3",
      "line_index": 144,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "4c73a3a7",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "下僕のクセに逃げるってどういう了見よっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "147.1",
      "line_index": 147,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "aedb1ed2",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "下僕なら下僕らしく、ひれ伏しながら挨拶の一つでもするってものでしょうが！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "150.0",
      "line_index": 150,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "62cc33bb",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "人のことを下僕下僕って、俺はそんなもになった覚えなんて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.1",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "eef466e1",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "うるさいっ！　口答えするなって言ってるでしょ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "158.1",
      "line_index": 158,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "58792a3d",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "はぁ～……覚えの悪いあんたには、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "158.3",
      "line_index": 158,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "58792a3d",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "海賊団としての礼儀を一から教えてあげる必要がありそうね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "161.1",
      "line_index": 161,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3452e478",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "下僕は下僕らしくあるようにねっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "164.0",
      "line_index": 164,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9ebf134e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "だから下僕扱い──",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "169.1",
      "line_index": 169,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d3db806e",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "お黙り！　返事はアイアイマム！　これだけよ！　ほら言いなさいっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "172.0",
      "line_index": 172,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1b57558c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "だっ誰がそんなこと──",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "178.1",
      "line_index": 178,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d8c714b6",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "──返事は！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.0",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5c04e5a2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ううっ！？　あ、アイアイ、ま、マム……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "186.1",
      "line_index": 186,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7916219f",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "ふっふ～ん♪　よろしい♪　少しはわかってきたみたいね。あはははっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "193.0",
      "line_index": 193,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a763c993",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（くう……い、勢いで言ってしまった……！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "197.0",
      "line_index": 197,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ec54b733",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（でも今すごい良い匂いしたな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "197.2",
      "line_index": 197,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ec54b733",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "まぁ、アイディルって黙っていれば可愛いし、当然なのかも……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "202.1",
      "line_index": 202,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1ad9c203",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "そもそもあんたってさ、海賊にどんなイメージ持っているわけ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "202.3",
      "line_index": 202,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "1ad9c203",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "なんか全然怖がっていないし、もしかしてあたしのこと舐めてる？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "205.0",
      "line_index": 205,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ca07a7b0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いや、舐めているつもりはないけどさ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "209.0",
      "line_index": 209,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4b985193",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（可愛いが優先されて、怖い印象は全然ないんだよなぁ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "209.2",
      "line_index": 209,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4b985193",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "めんどくさい性格だけど話はしやすいし）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "213.1",
      "line_index": 213,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f6eafb69",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "あんたの持っている海賊のイメージってどんなの？　教えてよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "216.0",
      "line_index": 216,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "999fff01",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "海賊のイメージ……ねぇ……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "216.2",
      "line_index": 216,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "999fff01",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うーん……酒を飲んで、お宝集めして、商船を襲う……そんなイメージかなぁ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "220.1",
      "line_index": 220,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b8bb4006",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "うんうん、その通り、何よ、ちゃんと海賊のことわかっているじゃないの♪",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "223.0",
      "line_index": 223,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f3872578",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あと髭面の船長？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "228.1",
      "line_index": 228,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "277293d0",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "はぁっ！？　何よ、そのイメージは！　どっから髭なんて出てきたのよ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "231.0",
      "line_index": 231,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a8f6d55c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いや、俺の持っている海賊の印象ってそんなもんで……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "231.2",
      "line_index": 231,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a8f6d55c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あと片手がフックで、いっつもガハハ笑っている感じ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "236.1",
      "line_index": 236,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c1f83ac4",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "何よそれ！　あたしと全然違うじゃない！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "239.0",
      "line_index": 239,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "25afd565",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そんなこと言われてもなぁ……ああ、あと略奪行為で殺しは日常で、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "239.2",
      "line_index": 239,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "25afd565",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "酔ったきまぐれで仲間を処刑したり……そんな血生臭い印象もあるかな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "243.1",
      "line_index": 243,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9319603e",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "は……！？　だ、誰もそんなことしないわよ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "246.1",
      "line_index": 246,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "cc8b6818",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "そんな恐ろしいイメージを持つな！　下僕のくせにっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "249.0",
      "line_index": 249,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "db3ce97b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "な、なんでそんな怒るんだよっ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "249.2",
      "line_index": 249,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "db3ce97b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そもそもアイディルが海賊のイメージを言えって言ったんだろうが",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "253.1",
      "line_index": 253,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b04acf3d",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "うるさいっ！　口答えは禁止！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "253.3",
      "line_index": 253,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "b04acf3d",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "あと恐ろしいイメージを持つのも禁止！　わかったわねっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "256.0",
      "line_index": 256,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "87b93e9b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……もしかしてさ、アイディルってそういうのできなかったりする？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "261.1",
      "line_index": 261,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c53601df",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "はぁ？　そういうのって何よ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "264.0",
      "line_index": 264,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "812398f7",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いや、俺がさっき言った血生臭い行為",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "268.1",
      "line_index": 268,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "935c5d9b",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "べ、別にできるけど……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "268.3",
      "line_index": 268,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "935c5d9b",
      "speaker": "アイディル",
      "ja": "というか、そんなの日常だし？　海賊なら当たり前ってヤツよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
